Name: Average time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Checklist Completed after the execution of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-Initial Reviewer Selection in variants that include reviewer assignment delays
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Elapsed time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and Plagiarism Originality Report Completed compared to the elapsed time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Average waiting time to SW-Checklist Completed after Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in cases where Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total resolution time of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in submission-to-rejection variants versus submission-to-acceptance variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Time of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed relative to the duration of the entire pre-review phase (from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Minimum time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-AE Assign Reviewers in variants involving multiple reviewer invitations and declines
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Average time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and the first occurrence of any SW-Reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-Reviewer Agreed, SW-Reviewer Declined, SW-Reviewer No Response)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total time it takes SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to begin after Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in high-complexity variants (those with frequency = 1 and performance > 30,000,000)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Cycle Time of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed measured as the interval between its start (implied by prior activity completion) and its timestamp, inferred from Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-Reviewer Agreed in cases where SW-Reviewer Agreed eventually occurs, highlighting its role as a gateway to substantive review
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Elapsed time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-EIC Reject in direct rejection paths versus paths leading to revision or acceptance
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'
